Document: VisualShaderNodeSwitch
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeswitch.rst
Summary: The op_type property and its accessor methods for defining operand and return value types in VisualShaderNodeSwitch.

OpType op_type = 0

Method: set_op_type(value: OpType)
Method: get_op_type() → OpType

This property defines the type of operands and returned value. The OpType enum determines how the shader node processes input data and what type of value it outputs. The default value is 0, which corresponds to the first enum variant.